name: S K I M A S K
description:
"hanging out the window, money on my mental"
life is a lick, I'm here for the stick up

Serving as my first music NFT offering, Skimask is a collaboration between myself, German producer 46Brock, photographer Mahdi Atif, and illustrator Rodney Johnson. The collector of this NFT will also be gifted an embroidered, 1-of-1 skimask as a token of appreciation for the support.

Skimask Lyrics:

[hook]
Don’t know what they into
Hanging out the window
Money on my mental
I done switched the tempo
Up there like crescendo
I can make a hundred off an instrumental
I can make it rain every other day
Tell me what you into
She asking my name like she want the fame
But don’t want the issues

[verse 1]
50 below
When I walk in it froze
Niggas acting like hoes
But they talk on the low
Respect isn’t given
Young Nigga it’s chose
you ain’t the type who gon get what he owed
I done been low but I’m back up again
I had to rack up and stack up the wins
I had to reshape the circles I’m in
We know you only as good as yo friends
I got some money to dump, numbers to punch
I make a call and they coming for lunch
Packing a bag like we out on the run
Taking a flight to laguna for brunch
Gave em the keys
Niggas be watching and hating on me
Talking bout everything they ain’t achieve
Hard to believe you was just on the team

(Hook 2x)

[verse 2]

I ain’t got nothing for you when you come thru

Know what it was
